preference.name: NX_ETS_NXTRANSDIRECT_PRIORITY
preference.preference_description: Defines the the asynchronous JT translation request priority for piece parts and assemblies. This option is applicable when the asynchronous JT translation using nxtransdirect translator is enabled. The pattern {3,1} specifies priority-3 for piece parts and priority-1 for assemblies where 3-High, 2-Medium, 1-Low.
